The font used in dlyg is Mom's Typewriter by Christoph Mueller
(http://users.cuci.nl/nonsuch/main.htm), which is available 
http://www.dafont.com/moms-typewriter.font?fpp=50

The torn paper brush was created by Marko Dimic and is available
at http://tricorndesign.deviantart.com/art/Torn-Paper-Brushes-178409431?q=boost%3Apopular%20in%3Aresources%2Fapplications%2Fpsbrushes%20torn%20paper&qo=2
